OL,3,CHoliday scammers stole more than #11
OL,4,Cmillion from Brits last year
OL,6,FFigures released by Action Fraud as
OL,7,Fpart of a new campaign against holiday
OL,8,Fscams show that typically more than a
OL,9,Fdozen people each day are being
OL,10,Fscammed.
OL,12,FFor those who fall victim to the
OL,13,Fincreasingly sophisticated stings, the
OL,14,Fcost can be high - averaging #1,844.
OL,16,FFor some, the losses go beyond
OL,17,Ffinancial - as they end up arriving at
OL,18,Fthe accommodation they thought they'd
OL,19,Fbooked - only to discover it's a con.
