OL,6,FOverall, holiday scams reported to
OL,7,FAction Fraud took more than #11
OL,8,Fmillion from victims last year.
OL,10,FFor years, digital technology has
OL,11,Fhelped customers book holidays - but
OL,12,Fit's also a big help to the criminals.
OL,14,FOne holiday industry insider told me
OL,15,Fit used to be quite easy to spot fake
OL,16,Fholiday booking sites - but now it's
OL,17,Fhard. Police forces report that around
OL,18,Fhalf of the scams involve social media.
OL,20,FWe've gathered some of the important
OL,21,Ftips here:
